com.camerontec.util.concurrent

Class SynchronousResult<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.util.concurrent.SynchronousResult<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The result type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Promise<T>, Future<T>

    public final class SynchronousResult<T>
extends Object
implements Promise<T>, Future<T>
    Synchronous result implementation.

    Instances of this class are designed to be used when an asynchronous API exists on top of a synchronous implementation. In that case there is no need to the caller to ever be blocked awaiting a response.
